Visconti e Nobile | 148 followers on LinkedIn. Business & Tax Consulting focused on the creation and protection of business value | Physical proximity to the customer is an essential experience for devising consulting solutions that create and protect business value over time. Physically alongside the company and without the limits associated with large structures, the Firm builds strategies of value thanks to the multiple skills of a widely diversified network of professional partners. Our activity focuses on the following points: 
- Business Consulting 
- Tax Consulting 
- Outsourcing
